099F B7FF01           (         lisp.asm):00857                     sta     ACIA_DATA
09A2 39               (         lisp.asm):00858                     rts
                      (         lisp.asm):00859         
                      (         lisp.asm):00860         ; key_blocking: read one char from ACIA into A.  Blocks.  Echoes.
